headline: The Collab You Didn't Know You Needed: New HERSHEY'S KISSES Cinnamon Toast Crunch™ Flavored Candies Hit Shelves Nationwide
summary: A nostalgic twist on the classic Hershey's Kisses has made its way into retailers across the U.S. with the official launch of Hershey's Kisses Cinnamon Toast Crunch™ flavored candies. If there's one thing 75%1 of Gen Z and Millennials can agree on, it's that out-of-the-ordinary flavor mashups are the snacks they're reaching for. That's why the two brands have joined forces to create the ultimate snack for the whole family to enjoy.
